2. Human in the loop review for outbound emails (especially during testing phase)
3. Quick onboarding/offboarding email addresses for agents within minutes
4. Websocket for local agents and at-least-once webhook delivery for Cloud agents&lt;p&gt;Not yet: DMARC (only SPF/DKIM today), scoped API keys, HA/multi-region (single VM + single Postgres), app-layer email data encryption, compliance attestations (SOC 2/HIPAA).&lt;p&gt;GitHub: &lt;a href="https://github.com/Mnexa-AI/e2a" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://github.com/Mnexa-AI/e2a&lt;/a&gt;
Hosted: &lt;a href="https://e2a.dev/" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://e2a.dev/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Appreciate any feedback / contributions.&lt;/p&gt;
